Package: staggeredpower
Title: Power Analysis for Staggered Difference-in-Differences Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zubin", "Jelveh", email = "zjelveh@umd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for conducting power analysis in staggered difference-in-differences 
    designs. Implements methods for enforcing parallel trends assumptions and simulating 
    treatment effects to assess statistical power.
